briefdescription.para: Class object for stock and write metadatas for the ICD6's Root Group.

detaileddescription.para: Usage: This class need as parameter all metadata for the ICD6( or dynamic spectrum)'s Root Group. The function stockRootMetadata stocks Root metadata in private attributes, and the function writeRootMetadata write them in the Root Group of the hdf5 file in output
